verbose_text: However, the levels of BRAP (124-569), remaining at the end of the 90-min reaction (XREF_FIG), detected as non ubiquitylated BRAP (124-569) using WB with an anti-BRAP antibody, were higher for S65D-M1-Ub4 than for wild-type M1-Ub4; this suggests that the auto-ubiquitylation efficiency of BRAP was lower in the reaction using S65D-M1-Ub4 than that using WT M1-Ub4.
